## Basic Usage

### Utility-First Approach

```html
<!-- Good: Tailwind utilities -->
<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow">
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Card Title</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Card content goes here.</p>
  <button class="bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
    Click Me
  </button>
</div>

<!-- Avoid: Custom CSS classes when Tailwind can do it -->
<div class="custom-card">
  <h2 class="custom-heading">Card Title</h2>
  <p class="custom-text">Card content.</p>
  <button class="custom-button">Click Me</button>
</div>
```

